{
    "495:0": "purapraveśaparivartaḥ |",
    "495:1": "tatra bhagavān punarapi candraprabhaṃ kumārabhūtamāmantrayate sma-tasmāttarhi kumāra pratipattisāro bhaviṣyāmītyevaṃ tvayā kumāra sadā śikṣitavyam |",
    "495:2": "tat kasya hetoḥ?",
    "495:3": "pratipattisārasya hi kumāra bodhisattvasya mahāsattvasya na durlabhā bhavatyanuttarā samyaksaṃbodhiḥ,",
    "495:4": "kiṃ punarayaṃ samādhiḥ |",
    "495:5": "atha khalu candraprabhaḥ kumārabhūta utthāyāsanādekāṃsamuttarāsaṅgaṃ kṛtvā dakṣiṇaṃ jānumaṇḍalaṃ pṛthivyāṃ pratiṣṭhāpya yena bhagavāṃstenāñjaliṃ praṇamya bhagavantametadavocat-āścaryaṃ bhagavan yāvat subhāṣitā ceyaṃ bhagavatā bodhisattvānāṃ mahāsattvānāmavavādānuśāsanī sarvabodhisattvaśikṣā deśitā svākhyātā suprajñaptā |",
    "495:6": "sarvatathāgatagocaro'yaṃ bhagavan yatra abhūmiḥ sarvaśrāvakapratyekabuddhānāṃ kaḥ punarvādo'nyatīrthikānām ?",
    "495:7": "pratipattisārāśca vayaṃ bhagavan bhaviṣyāmaḥ anapekṣāḥ kāyajīvite ca bhūtvā tathāgatasyānu śikṣiṣyāmahe |",
    "495:8": "tat kasya hetoḥ ?",
    "495:9": "śikṣitukāmāśca vayaṃ bhagavaṃstathāgatasya,",
    "495:10": "abhisaṃboddhukāmā vayaṃ bhagavannanuttarāṃ samyaksaṃbodhim |",
    "495:11": "arthikā vayaṃ bhagavan anuttarāyāḥ samyaksaṃbodheḥ |",
    "495:12": "vidhvaṃsayitukāmāśca vayaṃ bhagavan māraṃ pāpīyāṃsam |",
    "495:13": "mocayitukāmā vayaṃ bhagavan sarvasattvān sarvabhayebhyaḥ sarvaduḥkhebhyaḥ |",
    "495:14": "adhivāsayatu me bhagavān śvastane mama gṛhe bhaktaṃ bhoktuṃ sārdhaṃ bodhisattvagaṇena sārdhaṃ bhikṣusaṃghena cānukampāmupādāya |",
    "495:15": "adhivāsayati sma bhagavāṃścandraprabhasya kumārabhūtasya tūṣṇīṃbhāvena śvastane gṛhe bhaktaṃ bhoktuṃ sārdhaṃ bodhisattvagaṇena bhikṣusaṃghena cānukampāmupādāya |",
    "495:16": "atha khalu candraprabhaḥ kumārabhūto bhagavatastūṣṇīṃbhāvenādhivāsanaṃ viditvā utthāyāsanādekāṃsamuttarāsaṅgaṃ kṛtvā bhagavataḥ pādau śirasābhivandya bhagavantaṃ triḥ pradakṣiṇīkṛtya bhagavato'ntikāt prākrāmat ||",
    "495:17": "atha khalu candaprabhaḥ kumārabhūto yena rājagṛhaṃ mahānagaraṃ yena ca svakaṃ niveśanaṃ tenopasamakrāmat |",
    "495:18": "upasaṃkramya candraprabhaḥ svagṛhaṃ prāviśat |",
    "495:19": "praviśya ca tāmeva rātriṃ prabhūtaṃ praṇītaṃ khādanīyaṃ bhojanīyaṃ svādanīyamabhisaṃskārayati sma |",
    "495:20": "śatarasaṃ ca bhojanaṃ saṃpādya tasyā eva rātryā atyayena rājagṛhaṃ mahānagaraṃ susiktaṃ susaṃmṛṣṭaṃ muktakusumābhikīrṇaṃ gandhaghaṭikānirghūpitamucchritacchatradhvajapatākaṃ dhūpanadhūpitaṃ vitānavitatamavasaktapaṭṭadāmakalāpaṃ sarathyāntarāpaṇamapagatapāṣāṇaśarkarakaṭhallaṃ vicitrapuṣpābhikīrṇaṃ candanacūrṇābhikīrṇaṃ gavākṣatoraṇaniryūhapañjarajālārdhacandrasamalaṃkṛtaṃ candanānuliptamakārṣīt |",
    "495:21": "sarvāvantaṃ nagaramutpalakumudapadmapuṇḍarīkābhyavakīrṇamakārṣīt |",
    "495:22": "svaṃ ca gṛhaṃ sarvālaṃkāravyūhitamakārṣīt |",
    "495:23": "atha khalu candraprabhaḥ kumārabhūta imānevaṃrupān nagaravyūhān gṛhavyūhān bhojanavyūhān samalaṃkṛtya rājagṛhānmahānagarānniṣkramya yena gṛdhrakūṭaparvato yena bhagavāṃstenopasamakrāmat |",
    "495:24": "upasaṃkramya bhagavantaṃ triḥ pradakṣiṇīkṛtya ekānte'sthāt |",
    "495:25": "ekānte sthitaḥ candraprabhaḥ kumārabhūto bhagavataḥ kālamārocayāmāsa-kālo bhagavan,",
    "495:26": "kālaḥ sugata,",
    "495:27": "siddhaṃ bhaktaṃ yasyedānīṃ kālaṃ manyase |",
    "495:28": "atha khalu bhagavān utthāyāsanāt kalyameva nivāsya pātracīvaramādāya mahatā bhikṣusaṃghena sārdhaṃ paripūrṇena bhikṣuśatasahasreṇa saṃbahulaiśca bodhisattvairmahāsattvaiḥ parivṛtaḥ puraskṛto'nekaiśca devanāgayakṣagandharvāsuragaruḍakinnaramahoragamanuṣyāmanuṣyaśatasahasraiḥ pūjyamāno'bhiṣṭūyamāno mahatā buddhānubhāvena mahatā buddhaprātihāryeṇa mahatā buddheryāpathena raśmikoṭiniyutaśatasahasrairniścaradbhirnānātūryaśatasahasraiḥ puṣpagandhamālyavilepanacūrṇacīvaraiḥ pravarṣadbhiryena rājagṛhaṃ mahānagaraṃ tenopasaṃkrāmati sma |",
    "495:29": "candraprabhasya kumārabhūtasya niveśane prakṣiptaśca bhagavatā dakṣiṇaścakraratnasamalaṃkṛtaḥ aparimitakuśalasaṃcitapādaratna indrakīle,",
    "495:30": "atha tāvadeva tasmin mahānagare anekāni āścaryādbhutāni prātihāryāṇi saṃdṛśyante sma |",
    "495:31": "iyamatra dharmatā |",
    "495:32": "tatredamucyate -",
    "495:33": "puravara praviśanti nāyakasmin",
    "495:34": "caraṇavaru sthapitaśca indrakīle |",
    "495:35": "calati vasumatī śirīya tasya",
    "495:36": "pramudita bhonti purottamasmi sattvāḥ || 1 ||",
    "495:37": "ye naraḥ kṣudhitāḥ pipāsitā vā",
    "495:38": "na bhavati teṣa jighatsa tasmi kāle |",
    "495:39": "apagata bhavatī kṣughā pipāsā",
    "495:40": "yada jinu nikṣipatīndrakīli pādam || 2 ||",
    "495:41": "tatha puna nara ye bhavanti andhāḥ",
    "495:42": "śrotravihīna anātha alpapuṇyāḥ |",
    "495:43": "sarvi pratilabhanti cakṣu śrotraṃ",
    "495:44": "yada jinu nikṣipatīndrakīli pādam || 3 ||",
    "495:45": "yamaviṣaye ye keci bhonti pretāḥ",
    "495:46": "suduḥkhita kheṭasiṃghāṇakabhojanāśāḥ |",
    "495:47": "sarvi sukhita bhonti ābhaspṛṣṭā",
    "495:48": "yada jinu nikṣipatīndrakīli pādam || 4 ||",
    "495:49": "śailaśikharaśṛṅgaparvatāśca",
    "495:50": "tatha varapādapaśālakarṇikārāḥ |",
    "495:51": "sarvi abhinamanti yena buddho",
    "495:52": "yada jinu nikṣipatīndrakīli pādam || 5 ||",
    "495:53": "sanagaranigamā sasāgarāntā",
    "495:54": "pracali vasuṃdhari ṣaḍ-vikāra sarvā |",
    "495:55": "na bhavati viheṭha kasyapi ceha",
    "495:56": "yada jinu nikṣipatīndrakīli pādam || 6 ||",
    "495:57": "marumanujakumbhāṇḍarākṣasāśca",
    "495:58": "nabhaḥsthita tuṣṭa udagracittāḥ |",
    "495:59": "chatra dhariya ca lokanāyakasya",
    "495:60": "paramaprīṇita janetva bodhichandam || 7 ||",
    "495:61": "śrūyati ca manojña vādyaśabda-",
    "495:62": "stūryasahasra aghaṭṭitā raṇanti |",
    "495:63": "pramuditāstada bhonti sarvasattvā",
    "495:64": "yada jinu nikṣipatīndrakīli pādam || 8 ||",
    "495:65": "vṛkṣaśatasahasra onamanti",
    "495:66": "sarvi prapuṣpita bhonti tasmi kāle |",
    "495:67": "devaśatasahasra antarīkṣe",
    "495:68": "pūja karonti amānuṣī jinasya || 9 ||",
    "495:69": "ṛṣabhagaṇa tadā nadanti hṛṣṭā",
    "495:70": "hayadviradādhipatī pravṛddhakāyāḥ |",
    "495:71": "mṛgapatayo nadanti siṃhanādaṃ",
    "495:72": "yada jinu nikṣipatīndrakīli pādam || 10 ||",
    "495:73": "mahīpataya ye keci bhūmipālā",
    "495:74": "diśividiśāsu ca āgatā bhavanti |",
    "495:75": "dharaṇitali patanti hṛṣṭacittā",
    "495:76": "dṛṣṭu jinasya śirīmimamevarūpām || 11 ||",
    "495:77": "anye abhiṣṭuvanti lokanātham",
    "495:78": "apari kṣipanti jinasya puṣpavṛṣṭim |",
    "495:79": "apari daśanakhāñjaliṃ karitvā",
    "495:80": "aho jinu kāruṇiko bhaṇanti vācam || 12 ||",
    "495:81": "keci vara kṣipanti muktahārān",
    "495:82": "bahuvidha ābharaṇān janetva prītim |",
    "495:83": "cīvara ratanān kṣipanti anye",
    "495:84": "atuliyu agru jinatva bodhicittam || 13 ||",
    "495:85": "keci vara kṣipanti hemajālaṃ",
    "495:86": "apari punarmukhaphullakaṃ kṣipanti |",
    "495:87": "keci vara kṣipanti hemaniṣkāṃ-",
    "495:88": "statha apare parihārakān kṣipanti || 14 ||",
    "495:89": "kaṭakavara kṣipanti keci tatra",
    "495:90": "apari keyūra kṣipanti ratnacitrān |",
    "495:91": "ambara kusumān kṣipanti anye",
    "495:92": "citta janetva ' siyāṃ vayaṃ pi buddhāḥ' || 15 ||",
    "495:93": "apari naraḥ kṣipanti hemacitrāṃ -",
    "495:94": "statha maṇisūtravarān prasannacittāḥ |",
    "495:95": "keci ca ratanajālakaṃ kṣipanti",
    "495:96": "dvāri yadā sthitu bhoti lokanāthaḥ || 16 ||",
    "495:97": "paramaduḥkhita ye bhavanti sattvā",
    "495:98": "bahuvidhupadruvu śokaśalya prāptāḥ |",
    "495:99": "sarvi sukhasamarpitā bhavanti",
    "495:100": "puruṣavarasya śirīya nāyakasya || 17 ||",
    "495:101": "parabhṛtaśukasārikāmayūrā-",
    "495:102": "stathapi ca sārasacāṣahaṃsakrauñcāḥ |",
    "495:103": "sarvi dvijagaṇā nabhe sthihitvā",
    "495:104": "paramamanojñarutāni vyāharanti || 18 ||",
    "495:105": "pramudita tada bhonti pakṣisaṃghā",
    "495:106": "madhuramanojñarutaṃ pramuñcamānāḥ |",
    "495:107": "rāgu tatha samenti doṣamohaṃ",
    "495:108": "ye ca śṛṇanti manojña pakṣiśabdān || 19 ||",
    "495:109": "śruṇiya rañjanīya sattvakoṭyaḥ",
    "495:110": "sarvi ca labhanti kṣāntimānulomām |",
    "495:111": "tāṃśca sugata vyākaroti sarvān",
    "495:112": "bhaviṣyatha yūya jinā anāgatāśca || 20 ||",
    "495:113": "na bhavati kileśu tasmi kāle",
    "495:114": "sarvi sagaurava bhonti dharmarāje |",
    "495:115": "apagatabhayadoṣamohajālāḥ",
    "495:116": "praṇipatitāḥ sugatamabhiṣṭuvantaḥ || 21 ||",
    "495:117": "paśyiya tada rūpa nāyakasya",
    "495:118": "spṛha janayanti varasmi buddhajñāne |",
    "495:119": "kada vaya labhe jñānamevarūpam",
    "495:120": "āśayu jñātva jino'sya vyākaroti || 22 ||",
    "495:121": "raśmi śatasahasra niścaranti",
    "495:122": "ekaikataḥ sugatasya romakūpāt |",
    "495:123": "taduttari yatha gaṅgavālikā vā",
    "495:124": "na pi ca nimittu gṛhītu śakyu tāsām || 23 ||",
    "495:125": "sūryaprabha na bhāntiṃ tasmi kāle",
    "495:126": "na pi maṇi nāgni na sarvadevatānām |",
    "495:127": "sarvi prabha na bhānti tasmi kāle",
    "495:128": "yada praviśanta puraṃ vibhāti buddhaḥ || 24 ||",
    "495:129": "padmaśatasahasra prādurbhūtā",
    "495:130": "dharaṇitu koṭisahasrapatra śuddhāḥ |",
    "495:131": "yatra daśabalaḥ sthapeti pādaṃ",
    "495:132": "mārga gataḥ sugato mahāgaṇena || 25 ||",
    "495:133": "aśuci kalimalā na bhonti tasmi kāle",
    "495:134": "nagaravaraṃ praviśanti nāyakasmin |",
    "495:135": "nagaru surabhi sarvi dhūpanena",
    "495:136": "gandha manojña pravāyate samantāt || 26 ||",
    "495:137": "vīthi nagari tada bhoti sarvā",
    "495:138": "apagataloṣṭakaṭhalla sikta gandhaiḥ |",
    "495:139": "puṇya daśalabasya evarūpā",
    "495:140": "vividha vikīrṇa bhavanti muktapuṣpāḥ || 27 ||",
    "495:141": "yakṣa śatasahasra raudracittāḥ",
    "495:142": "kanakanibhaṃ dvipadendru dṛṣṭva buddham |",
    "495:143": "janayi vipulu nāyakasmi premaṃ",
    "495:144": "śaraṇamupeti ca buddhadharmasaṃghān || 28 ||",
    "495:145": "ye ca devaśatasahasra koṭiyo vā",
    "495:146": "upagata sarvi narendradarśanāya |",
    "495:147": "varṣati sugatasya puṣpavarṣaṃ",
    "495:148": "gaganatale ca sthihanti muktapuṣpāḥ || 29 ||",
    "495:149": "ye manuja kṣipī jinasya puṣpaṃ",
    "495:150": "gaganatale bhavatīti puṣpachatram |",
    "495:151": "ye puna kusumān kṣipanti devā",
    "495:152": "dharaṇitale stṛta bhonti divyapuṣpāḥ || 30 ||",
    "495:153": "na bhavati kadāci dṛṣṭva tṛptī",
    "495:154": "devamanuṣyakubhāṇḍarākṣasānām |",
    "495:155": "yada daśabalu dṛṣṭva lokanāthaṃ",
    "495:156": "pramudita bhonti udagrakalyacittāḥ || 31 ||",
    "495:157": "na manasi tada bhonti divyapuṣpā",
    "495:158": "na ca puna vismayu jāyate ca tatra |",
    "495:159": "yada puruṣavarasya kāyu dṛṣṭvā",
    "495:160": "tuṣṭa bhavanti udagra sarvasattvāḥ || 32 ||",
    "495:161": "brahma daśabalasya dakṣiṇeno",
    "495:162": "tatha puna vāmatu śakra devarājā |",
    "495:163": "gaganatalagatā analpa devakoṭyaḥ",
    "495:164": "puruṣavarasya janenti citrikāram || 33 ||",
    "495:165": "parivṛta jinu devadānavehi",
    "495:166": "marumanujāna śiriṃ grasitva sarvām |",
    "495:167": "dharaṇi kramatalehi citrayanto",
    "495:168": "praviśi puraṃ bhagavānnimantraṇāya || 34 ||",
    "495:169": "kusumita anuvyañjanehi kāye",
    "495:170": "yatha gaganaṃ paripūrṇa tārakehi |",
    "495:171": "pratapati sthitu rājamārgi buddha-",
    "495:172": "ścandro nabhaḥstha yathaiva pūrṇimāsyām || 35 ||",
    "495:173": "maṇiratanu yathā viśuddhu śreṣṭhaṃ",
    "495:174": "vyapagatadoṣamalaṃ prabhāsamānam |",
    "495:175": "diśi vidiśi pramuñci ābha śuddhāṃ",
    "495:176": "tatha jinu bhāsati sarvalokadhātum || 36 ||",
    "495:177": "parivṛtu jinu devadānavehi",
    "495:178": "praviśati rājagṛhaṃ narāṇa śreṣṭhaḥ |",
    "495:179": "dharaṇi kramatalehi citrayanto",
    "495:180": "praviśati candraprabhasya gehi buddhaḥ || 37 ||",
    "495:181": "puruvaru samalaṃkṛtaṃ samantād",
    "495:182": "bahu dhvaja koṭisahasra ucchitātra |",
    "495:183": "gandhavaravilipta sarvabhūmī",
    "495:184": "sumanaḥprakīrṇa tathaiva vārṣikāram || 38 ||",
    "495:185": "yada sugatu kathāṃ katheti nātho",
    "495:186": "vīthigato manujān kṛpāyamānaḥ |",
    "495:187": "nirmitu jinu tatra nirmiṇitvā",
    "495:188": "vitarati teṣu praṇīta buddhadharmān || 39 ||",
    "495:189": "daśaniyuta jināna nirmitāna",
    "495:190": "kanakanibhā abhirūpa darśanīyā |",
    "495:191": "parivṛtu jinu buddhu nirmitehi",
    "495:192": "vitarati śūnyata śānta buddhabodhim || 40 ||",
    "495:193": "prāṇiśatasahasra taṃ śruṇitvā",
    "495:194": "praṇidadhi cittu varāgrabuddhajñāne |",
    "495:195": "kada vaya labhi jñānamevarūpaṃ",
    "495:196": "āśayu jñātva jino'sya vyākaroti || 41 ||",
    "495:197": "keci spṛha janenti tatra kāle",
    "495:198": "parama acintiya labdha tehi lābhāḥ |",
    "495:199": "yehi jinu nimantrito narendro",
    "495:200": "na ca paryanta sa teṣu dakṣiṇāyāḥ || 42 ||",
    "495:201": "keci punarupapādayi sucittaṃ",
    "495:202": "śvo vaya kāruṇikaṃ nimantrayāmaḥ |",
    "495:203": "hitakaramanukampakaṃ prajānāṃ",
    "495:204": "yasya sudurlabhu darśanaṃ bhaveṣu || 43 ||",
    "495:205": "keci sthita niryūhakhoṭake hi",
    "495:206": "subhagu vibhūṣitagātra premaṇīyāḥ |",
    "495:207": "divya daśabalasya muktapuṣpā-",
    "495:208": "ṇyavakirate'gru janitva bodhicittam || 44 ||",
    "495:209": "surucira vara campakasya mālāṃ",
    "495:210": "tatha atimuktaka gandhavarṣikāṃ ca |",
    "495:211": "apari puna kṣipanti paṭṭadāmān",
    "495:212": "parama niruttaru cittu saṃjanitvā || 45 ||",
    "495:213": "keci sthita gṛhe gṛhītapuṣpāḥ",
    "495:214": "paramavibhūṣitakāyu cīvarehi |",
    "495:215": "puṣpa vividhu gṛhītva paṭṭadāmān",
    "495:216": "pravarṣi yena jino mahānubhāvaḥ || 46 ||",
    "495:217": "padumakumudotpalān kṣipanti keci",
    "495:218": "apari kṣipanti viśiṣṭa hemapuṣpān |",
    "495:219": "maṇiratana kṣipanti keci tasmin",
    "495:220": "apari kṣipanti ca cūrṇa candanasya || 47 ||",
    "495:221": "aparimita bhavanti accharīyā",
    "495:222": "atuliya ye na ca śakyu kīrtanāya |",
    "495:223": "puravaru praviśanti nāyakasmin",
    "495:224": "bahujanakoṭya sthihiṃsu buddhajñāne || 48 ||",
    "495:225": "abṛha atapāśca dṛṣṭasattyāḥ",
    "495:226": "sudṛśa sudarśana ye ca anya devāḥ |",
    "495:227": "tatha punarakaniṣṭha vītarāgā",
    "495:228": "upagata sarvi narendradarśanāya || 49 ||",
    "495:229": "tatha śubhamarutāśca aprameyā",
    "495:230": "aparimita śubhā udagracittāḥ |",
    "495:231": "śubhakṛtsna niyutāśca aprameyā",
    "495:232": "upagata paśyitu nāyakaṃ maharṣim || 50 ||",
    "495:233": "aparimitu tathāpramāṇa-ābhā",
    "495:234": "tatha puna deva parītta ābha ye ca |",
    "495:235": "bahu niyuta ābhasvarāṇa tasmin",
    "495:236": "upagata paśyitu te'pi lokanātham || 51 ||",
    "495:237": "bahava śatasahasra pāriṣadyā-",
    "495:238": "statha puna brahmapurohitāḥ prasannāḥ |",
    "495:239": "bahuśata puna brahmakāyikānāṃ",
    "495:240": "upagata nāyakadarśanāya sarve || 52 ||",
    "495:241": "tatha puna paranirmitāpi devā-",
    "495:242": "statha nirmāṇaratiśca śuddhasattvāḥ |",
    "495:243": "pramudita tuṣitātha yāmadevā",
    "495:244": "upagata sarvi namasyamāna buddham || 53 ||",
    "495:245": "tridaśa apu ca śakra devarājā",
    "495:246": "apsarakoṭiśataiḥ sahāgato'tra |",
    "495:247": "kusumavarṣa saṃpravarṣamāṇo",
    "495:248": "upagata buddhamunīndradarśanāya || 54 ||",
    "495:249": "caturi caturdiśāsu lokapālā",
    "495:250": "vaiśravaṇo dhṛtarāṣṭra nāgarājā |",
    "495:251": "virūḍhaku virūpākṣu hṛṣṭacittā",
    "495:252": "upagata sarvi narendra te stuvantā || 55 ||",
    "495:253": "ailavila balavanta yakṣarājā",
    "495:254": "parivṛta yakṣaśatehi premajātaḥ |",
    "495:255": "gaganatali sthihitva hṛṣṭacittaḥ",
    "495:256": "kṣipati aneka vicitra puṣpavarṣam || 56 ||",
    "495:257": "apari punarananta māladhārī",
    "495:258": "vividha vicitra gṛhītva mālyagandhān |",
    "495:259": "sarvi saparivāra hṛṣṭacittāḥ",
    "495:260": "puruṣavarasya karonti tatra pūjām || 57 ||",
    "495:261": "bahava śata karoṭapāṇi yakṣā",
    "495:262": "api ca subhūṣi teṣa yakṣakanyāḥ |",
    "495:263": "sumadhura sumanojña yakṣavādyai-",
    "495:264": "stūryaśatehi karonti buddhapūjām || 58 ||",
    "495:265": "lalita-madhura-gīta-vāditasmin",
    "495:266": "sukuśalaiḥ saha kinnarīsahasraiḥ |",
    "495:267": "druma upagata gandhamādanāto",
    "495:268": "jinavaru pūjitu kinnarāṇa rājñā || 59 ||",
    "495:269": "śaṃbara bala vemacitra rāhu",
    "495:270": "dānavakanya sahasrapārivārāḥ |",
    "495:271": "asuragaṇa maharddhikāśca anye",
    "495:272": "upagata te ratanāni varṣamāṇāḥ || 60 ||",
    "495:273": "śataniyuta ananta rākṣasānāṃ",
    "495:274": "rākṣasakoṭiśatairupāsyamānāḥ |",
    "495:275": "pṛthu vividha vicitra muktapuṣpān",
    "495:276": "puruṣavarasya kṣipanti gauraveṇa ||61 ||",
    "495:277": "tathapi ca anavataptu nāgarājā",
    "495:278": "paramasuśikṣitāśca nāgakanyāḥ |",
    "495:279": "tūryaśatasahasra nādayantyo",
    "495:280": "upagata pūjana tatra lokanātham || 62 ||",
    "495:281": "pañcaśata anavataptu putrā",
    "495:282": "vipulu anuttaru jñāna prārthayantaḥ |",
    "495:283": "svajanaparivṛtā udagra bhūtvā",
    "495:284": "upagata pūjayituṃ svayaṃ svayaṃbhūm || 63 ||",
    "495:285": "tathapi ca apalālu nāgarājā",
    "495:286": "puruṣavarasya kṛtāñjaliḥ praṇamya |",
    "495:287": "vara rucira gṛhītva nāgapuṣpān",
    "495:288": "sthita gagane munirāja satkarontaḥ || 64 ||",
    "495:289": "tathapi ca mucilinda nāgarājā",
    "495:290": "prītamanāḥ parituṣṭa harṣajātaḥ |",
    "495:291": "vividha ratnamauktikaṃ gṛhītvā",
    "495:292": "upagami nāyaku abhikirantu tatra || 65 ||",
    "495:293": "tathapi ca kāliko'pi nāgarājā",
    "495:294": "upagatu mukhu tathāgatasya hṛṣṭacittaḥ |",
    "495:295": "vara rūcira gṛhītva ratnadāmān",
    "495:296": "puruṣavarasya pūja karitva śreṣṭhām || 66 ||",
    "495:297": "so'pi parama gauravaṃ janitvā",
    "495:298": "anusmaramāṇu guṇāṃstathāgatasya |",
    "495:299": "svajanaparivṛtaḥ sanāgasaṃgho",
    "495:300": "bahuvidhu bhāṣati varṇa nāyakasya || 67 ||",
    "495:301": "nandu tathā upanandu nāgarājā",
    "495:302": "tatha punastakṣaka kṛṣṇagautamau ca |",
    "495:303": "upagata jinu te namasyamānāḥ",
    "495:304": "praṇipatitāḥ sugatasya pādayorhi || 68 ||",
    "495:305": "upagata elapatru nāgarājā",
    "495:306": "parivṛta nāgaśatehi rocamānaḥ |",
    "495:307": "munivara jinu kāśyapaṃ smaranto",
    "495:308": "svaka upapatti apaśyi akṣaṇeṣu || 69 ||",
    "495:309": "aho ahu puri āsi kāṅkṣaprāpto",
    "495:310": "mayi puri cchinnu parittamelapatram |",
    "495:311": "so ahu upapannu akṣaṇasmin",
    "495:312": "na sukaru dharma vijānituṃ jinasya || 70 ||",
    "495:313": "kṣipra ahu jahitva nāgayoniṃ",
    "495:314": "parama jugupsitametu jantukāyam |",
    "495:315": "dharmamahu vijāni śāntibhāvaṃ",
    "495:316": "puruṣavareṇa ya jñātu bodhimaṇḍe || 71 ||",
    "495:317": "sāgara ahirājacakravartī",
    "495:318": "parivṛtu nāgatrikoṭisahasraiḥ |",
    "495:319": "varuṇa manasvī gṛhītva muktāhārān",
    "495:320": "upagatu te bhagavantu pūjanāya || 72 ||",
    "495:321": "kṣipta śila jinasya tatra yeno",
    "495:322": "gaganasthitena gṛhītva tasmi kāle |",
    "495:323": "rājagṛhi sa kimpilo'pi yakṣaḥ",
    "495:324": "purataḥ sthitaḥ sugatasya gauraveṇa || 73 ||",
    "495:325": "alakavatī samagra rājadhānī",
    "495:326": "śūnya abhūṣi na tatra kaści yakṣaḥ |",
    "495:327": "sarvi kriya karitva anyamanyaṃ",
    "495:328": "upagata paśyitu sarvalokanātham || 74 ||",
    "495:329": "tathapi ca kharakarṇa sūciromā",
    "495:330": "āṭavikastatha yakṣa bheṣakaśca |",
    "495:331": "haimavata śatagiriśca yakṣa",
    "495:332": "upagata gardabhako jinaṃ svayaṃbhūm || 75 ||",
    "495:333": "indraketu vikaṭaśca surūpo",
    "495:334": "vakkulu pañciku śākya pravṛddho |",
    "495:335": "ete pare'pi ca yakṣendra sahastā",
    "495:336": "upagata dhūpaghaṭaṃ parigṛhya || 76 ||",
    "495:337": "vikṛta bahu duḥsaṃsthitātmabhāvā",
    "495:338": "vigalita-ābharaṇā anekarūpāḥ |",
    "495:339": "bahava śatasahasra tasmi kāle",
    "495:340": "upagata tatra gṛhītva yakṣa puṣpān || 77 ||",
    "495:341": "jalanidhi nivasanti ye suparṇā",
    "495:342": "upagata brāhmaṇaveśa nirmiṇitvā |",
    "495:343": "mukuṭadhara vicitra darśanīyā",
    "495:344": "gaganasthitāḥ sugataṃ namasyamānāḥ || 78 ||",
    "495:345": "nagaraśata ye keci jambudvīpe",
    "495:346": "vanavihareṣu ya tatra devatāśca |",
    "495:347": "sarva nagaradevatāḥ samagrā",
    "495:348": "upagata pūja karonta nāyakasya || 79 ||",
    "495:349": "upagata vanadevatā anantā-",
    "495:350": "stathapi ca sarvi ya śailadevatāśca |",
    "495:351": "tathapi ca nadidevatāḥ samagrā",
    "495:352": "upagata pūja karonta nāyakasya || 80 ||",
    "495:353": "aṭavimaruṣu devatāśatāni",
    "495:354": "giriśikhareṣu ya devatā samagrāḥ |",
    "495:355": "utsa-sara-taḍāgadevatāśca",
    "495:356": "upagata sāgaradevatāśca buddham || 81 ||",
    "495:357": "deva-asura-nāga-yakṣa-saṃghā",
    "495:358": "garuḍa-mahoraga-kinnarāḥ kumbhāṇḍāḥ |",
    "495:359": "tathapi ca bahu pretapūtanāśco",
    "495:360": "puruṣavarasya karonti citrikāram || 82 ||",
    "495:361": "te'pi ca jinavare karitva pūjāṃ",
    "495:362": "nagaravaraṃ praviśanti nāyakasmin |",
    "495:363": "deva asuranāgayakṣarājā |",
    "495:364": "satatamatṛpta bhavanti darśanena || 83 ||",
    "495:365": "yatha purimabhaveṣu lokanāthaḥ",
    "495:366": "purimajineṣu akārṣi pūja śreṣṭhām |",
    "495:367": "puṇyaphalavipāka evarūpo",
    "495:368": "na ca janu tṛptu narendra paśyamānaḥ || 84 ||",
    "495:369": "meru tatha sumeru cakravālā",
    "495:370": "himagiristatha gandhamādanaśca |",
    "495:371": "āvaraṇā na te jinasya bhonti",
    "495:372": "ābha yadā jinu muñci buddhakṣetre || 85 ||",
    "495:373": "ye ca iha samudra buddhakṣetre",
    "495:374": "te'pi mahīya samāstadā bhavanti |",
    "495:375": "sarvamimu samantu buddhakṣetraṃ",
    "495:376": "samu bhavatī kusumehi saṃprakīrṇam || 86 ||",
    "495:377": "raśmi śatasahasra aprameyā",
    "495:378": "avakiri pādatalehi dharmarājā |",
    "495:379": "sarvi niraya śītalā bhavanti",
    "495:380": "dharmaduḥkha upanīta sukhaṃ ca vedayanti || 87 ||",
    "495:381": "dharma daśabala saṃprabhāṣi tatro",
    "495:382": "marumanujāna viśuddha bhoti cakṣuḥ |",
    "495:383": "prāṇi śatasahasra aprameyā",
    "495:384": "niyata bhavanti ca sarvi buddhajñāne || 88 ||",
    "495:385": "bahu imi sugatasya pratihāryā",
    "495:386": "na sukaru vaktu ca kalpakoṭiyebhiḥ |",
    "495:387": "puravara praviśanti nāyakasmin",
    "495:388": "pramudita sarva jagajjinapraveśe || 89 ||",
    "495:389": "imi guṇa sugatasya aprameyā",
    "495:390": "naravṛṣabhasya guṇāgrapāragasya |",
    "495:391": "sarvaguṇaviśeṣapāragasya",
    "495:392": "śirasi namasyatha buddhapuṇyakṣetram || 90 ||",
    "495:393": "iti śrīsamādhirāje purapraveśaparivarto nāma daśamaḥ ||"
}